The evidence with the title 'Tuberculosis ' says Sep 18, 2018  ... In 2017 , 10 million people fell ill with tb, and 1.6 million died from the disease ( including 0.3 million among people with HIV).  ... TB is a leading killer of HIV- positive people .  ... Globally , tb incidence is falling at about 2% per year.  ... For prevention and treatment of infection and disease , to reduce deaths . 
